[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0899","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0899.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0616","title":"TFTP 服务开放导致信息泄露风险","description":"该CVE条目已被官方驳回（REJECT），原描述为\"TFTP服务正在运行\"。TFTP协议使用UDP 69端口，缺乏认证与加密机制，若未配置适当访问控制，运行中的TFTP服务可能被未经授权的攻击者利用进行文件读写操作，导致敏感信息泄露或任意文件上传。但由于该问题属于安全配置范畴而非代码层面的直接安全漏洞，因此不适用CVE编号体系，更适合归入CCE（通用配置枚举）管理。建议在非必要环境中禁用TFTP服务或限制访问来源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0616"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.373","remediation":"若业务不需要 TFTP 服务，建议在系统中停止并禁用 tftpd/tftp-hpa 服务（如 `systemctl disable tftp` 或移除 xinetd 配置）。如需使用，通过 iptables/firewalld 限制源 IP 访问 UDP 端口 69，仅允许受信任的管理网段连接，并考虑迁移至 SFTP/SCP 等加密文件传输协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0616.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0616","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0616.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/tftpd_detect.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0616.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000453.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/tftpd_detect.nasl","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0616.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0899.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0896","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0896.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0615","title":"SNMP 服务配置不当漏洞","description":"SNMP 服务在未配置访问控制或使用默认团体字符串时运行，远程攻击者可通过网络探测 UDP 端口 161/162 获取系统信息，包括网络拓扑、运行进程、系统配置和用户账户等敏感数据。该条目已被 NVD 拒绝，理由是此问题属于配置枚举范畴（CCE）而非直接安全漏洞，CVSS 为 0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0615"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.343","remediation":"如非必要，建议在系统服务中禁用 SNMP 服务 (snmpd)，减少攻击面。如需使用 SNMP，应升级至支持 SNMPv3 的版本并启用认证与加密（配置 authPriv），同时通过防火墙限制 UDP 161/162 端口的访问来源 IP，仅允许受信任的管理端连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0615","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Felix-sec/VulnDataExtr/blob/1f4ecda04291a8a4eb7e49189a9ee2bc026b8389/exact_keywords.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/1b758e4b71978ff973a6df1bc69fc70b932735fb/advisories/2000/02/EUVD-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0896.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0895","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0895.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0614","title":"通用 FTP 服务运行配置问题","description":"CVE-1999-0614 候选编号已被官方拒绝使用。该条目原始描述仅指出 FTP 服务正在运行，属于系统配置管理范畴，而非独立的安全漏洞。此类配置问题更适合在通用配置枚举（CCE）框架中收录，不具备传统的攻击向量、利用条件或安全影响。因此该编号不应被用于描述任何安全缺陷，也不构成对系统机密性、完整性和可用性的直接威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0614"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.310","remediation":"如非业务必要，建议关闭 FTP 服务（systemctl disable vsftpd/proftpd 或移除对应软件包）；如必须使用，应替换为 SFTP/FTPS 等加密传输协议，并配置防火墙仅允许受信 IP 访问（如 iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 21 -s 信任网段 -j ACCEPT），同时限制匿名登录、禁用 root 账户直接 FTP 登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0614","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/FTP%20server%20detection.plugin","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000451.txt","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml","https://github.com/Planet-Source-Code/marc-ruef-attack-tool-kit-3-0__1-57240/blob/96061f959b3cf8ad81fa5d603944798cc9f3304c/atk-3.0src/plugins/Macintosh%20OS%20X%20FTP%20server%20detection.plugin"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0895.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0894","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0894.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0613","title":"Sun RPC rpc.sprayd 服务本地权限提升漏洞","description":"rpc.sprayd 是 Unix 系统中用于网络喷发测试的 RPC 服务，运行于 100012 端口。由于 sprayd 守护进程以 root 权限运行且未对调用来源进行充分权限校验，本地攻击者可通过发送特制的 RPC 请求触发 sprayd 命令执行，将自身权限提升至 root。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris、HP-UX 及其他运行 rpc.sprayd 服务的类 Unix 系统，攻击者需拥有目标系统的本地 shell 访问权限。建议在非必要环境下禁用该服务或配置 RPC 访问控制列表。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0613"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.303","remediation":"立即禁用 rpc.sprayd 服务：在 Solaris 中执行 `svcadm disable svc:/network/rpc/spray:default` 或从 inetd.conf 中注释 sprayd 行并重启 inetd。同时配置防火墙/TCP Wrapper 限制 RPC 端口（111/32771-32800）仅允许可信网段访问，并安装操作系统厂商提供的 RPC 安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0613","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0613.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0613","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0613.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0894.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0891","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0891.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0611","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表键值配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中存在关键注册表项权限配置不当的安全漏洞。该漏洞允许远程攻击者利用不恰当的注册表键值，在目标系统上执行未授权操作，可能导致系统信息泄露、权限提升或拒绝服务。由于受影响注册表项涉及系统核心功能，攻击者一旦利用成功可完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响了 Windows NT 4.0 等早期版本，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0611"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.057","remediation":"检查注册表键 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\ 下关键子键的值权限，将不当值修改为默认安全配置；同时安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全更新，限制对注册表的远程访问权限，仅允许授权管理员通过 ACL 进行修改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0611","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0611.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0611","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0611.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86267/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0891.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0882","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0882.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0603","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 用户组成员权限配置不当漏洞","description":"在 Windows NT 系统中，用户账户可能被不当添加到高权限用户组（如 Administrators、Backup Operators、Domain Admins 等），导致低权限用户意外获得超出预期的系统访问权限。该漏洞源于系统组策略配置缺陷或管理失误，攻击者可利用已获取的低权限账户通过提权操作完全控制目标系统，影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0603"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.093","remediation":"立即审查所有域控制器和成员服务器上 Administrators、Backup Operators、Domain Admins、Power Users 等高权限组的成员列表，移除非必要或未授权的用户账户。通过「管理工具 → 计算机管理 → 本地用户和组 → 组」逐一检查各组成员，确保仅保留最小必要权限。部署安全基线策略（如 Microsoft Security Compliance Toolkit），定期审计组成员变更日志，并启用 Windows 审核策略中的「组成员管理」事件审计。升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本以利用细化的权限委派机制（如委派控制向导），避免将普通用户加入内置特权组。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0603","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0603","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0882.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0881","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0881.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0602","title":"多厂商网络入侵检测系统IP碎片重组绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理碎片化IP数据包时存在重组缺陷，攻击者可通过发送特制的碎片数据包绕过IDS检测规则。由于IDS无法正确还原原始载荷，恶意流量被误判为正常，导致攻击行为逃逸检测。该漏洞影响多种主流IDS产品，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用，且攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互。利用方式包括发送超小碎片、重叠偏移或超时碎片等绕过技术。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0602"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.983","remediation":"升级 IDS/IPS 引擎至最新版本（如 Snort ≥2.9.20、Suricata ≥7.0），启用 frag3 预处理器的分片重组功能；配置 `preprocessor frag3_global: max_frags 65536` 和 `preprocessor frag3_engine: policy windows`；对于无法升级的旧版系统，在网络层启用分片包拦截策略，仅允许完整 IP 包进入检测引擎。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0602","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0602.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8cxh-9x8c-5qr7/GHSA-8cxh-9x8c-5qr7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86251/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0881.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0880","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0880.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0601","title":"通用 网络入侵检测系统 TCP握手数据绕过漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0601 为网络入侵检测系统（IDS）中存在的TCP数据包处理缺陷。攻击者可在TCP三次握手过程中，将恶意载荷嵌入SYN、SYN-ACK等握手数据包的载荷字段或利用IP分片重组绕过IDS的深度包检测机制。由于早期IDS对TCP会话建立阶段的数据包缺乏完整重组与检测能力，导致攻击载荷可绕过安全审计直接到达目标主机。该漏洞影响了多种主流IDS产品的检测有效性，攻击者无需认证即可实施绕过，危害网络层面的安全监控体系。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0601"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.863","remediation":"启用 IDS/IPS 的 TCP 流重组功能（如 Snort 的 stream_tcp 预处理器或 Suricata 的内置流引擎），配置为自动重组所有 TCP 会话的完整载荷后再进行规则匹配；同时启用 TCP 规范化（normalization）以丢弃重叠分片或异常标志位的数据包，防止分片逃逸攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0601","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0601.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-45cf-cf6g-j6mm/GHSA-45cf-cf6g-j6mm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86244/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0880.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0879","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0600","title":"网络入侵检测系统 数据包校验和未验证漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理网络数据包时未验证校验和字段的正确性，远程攻击者可通过发送精心构造的畸形数据包绕过 IDS 的检测规则。由于 IDS 与目标主机对数据包的解析结果不一致，攻击者可利用该缺陷隐藏恶意流量，实现绕过告警的入侵行为。该漏洞影响多数未实现校验和验证的 IDS 产品，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0600"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.743","remediation":"在 IDS/IPS 配置中启用 IP 和 TCP 校验和验证功能（如 Snort 的 `config checksum_mode: all`），丢弃校验和错误的报文；升级至支持完整校验和检测的现代 IDS 版本（如 Suricata 7.x 或 Snort 3.x）；在边界防火墙上启用 TCP 校验和强制检查；同时在网络设备上启用 IP 选项过滤和分片重组校验，消除攻击者利用校验和绕过检测的路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0600","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0600.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86246/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0878","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0878.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0599","title":"通用 网络入侵检测系统 TCP异常序列号绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理包含异常TCP序列号的数据包时存在逻辑缺陷，攻击者可通过向目标网络发送精心构造的异常序列号数据包绕过IDS的检测与重组机制，导致恶意流量无法被正确识别和告警。该漏洞影响多种主流IDS产品，攻击者无需认证即可远程实施绕过攻击，严重削弱网络安全监控与威胁检测的有效性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0599"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.620","remediation":"升级支持 TCP 流重组（stream reassembly）的入侵检测系统，如 Suricata、Zeek（原名 Bro），并启用 `stream.reassembly` 引擎；禁用纯包级检测的旧式 IDS（如 Snort 1.x 传统模式）。配置 IDS 确保 TCP 分片重组策略与受保护目标主机一致（如设置 `target-based` 策略），避免插包（insertion）和逃逸（evasion）攻击。定期更新检测规则集以覆盖已知逃逸技术。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0599","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0599.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cgq4-92x7-335m/GHSA-cgq4-92x7-335m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86252/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0878.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0876","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0876.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0598","title":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）数据包乱序处理绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理乱序数据包时存在缺陷，无法正确重组和检测经过分片或乱序传输的攻击流量。远程攻击者可通过将恶意负载分散到多个乱序数据包中绕过 IDS 的检测规则，从而逃避安全监控。该漏洞影响多款主流网络入侵检测系统，可被用于隐藏端口扫描、漏洞利用等恶意行为，降低网络防御体系的有效性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0598"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.500","remediation":"配置IDS启用完整的TCP流重组（stream reassembly）功能，确保对乱序IP分片和TCP乱序报文进行正确重组后再执行规则匹配。同时启用分片超时与重组缓冲区限制，防止分片洪水绕过检测。建议使用支持应用层协议解析的现代IDS/IPS（如Snort/Suricata）并开启`stream5`或`stream`预处理模块。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0598","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0598.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hhgq-6w2j-9rc7/GHSA-hhgq-6w2j-9rc7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86249/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0876.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0874","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0874.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0597","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 账户策略登录时间限制绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 账户策略存在安全漏洞，当远程用户的登录时间到期后，系统未能强制断开其与服务器的连接，导致用户可在授权时段外继续访问系统资源。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，拥有有效域账户的远程攻击者可利用此问题绕过登录时间限制，在非授权时段持续访问服务器资源，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0597"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.383","remediation":"在 Windows NT 域用户管理器中选择\"规则(Policies)→账户(Account)\"，勾选\"当登录时数到期时强制断开远程用户与服务器的连接(Forcibly disconnect remote users from server when logon hours expire)\"。对于仍运行 Windows NT 的系统，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本，新版本默认启用该策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1343","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0597","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0597.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v2p7-wqpp-8h67/GHSA-v2p7-wqpp-8h67.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0597.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86258/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0874.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0872","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0872.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0596","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 日志文件大小与保留期限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 日志文件的最大大小或保留期限配置不当，可能导致日志文件无限制增长耗尽磁盘空间，引发拒绝服务；或日志过早轮转覆盖，导致关键安全事件记录丢失，影响事后审计与取证分析。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0596"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.267","remediation":"建议在 Windows NT 事件查看器中右键「事件日志」→「日志设置」，将日志最大大小根据磁盘容量设为 512MB 以上，回卷策略设为「按需要覆盖事件」而非「不要覆盖事件」。若仍使用旧版系统，应升级至 Windows Server 2003 及以上版本以获得完善的日志审计功能。作为临时缓解措施，可设置组策略定期归档并清理旧日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0596","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0596.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x2q8-w843-gwx7/GHSA-x2q8-w843-gwx7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0596.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86256/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0872.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0871","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0871.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0594","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 可移动介质未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统未对可移动介质驱动器（如软盘驱动器、光盘驱动器）的访问权限进行适当限制，导致未经授权的本地用户可通过物理接触或网络共享途径读取受保护的可移动介质中的敏感数据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，攻击者只需能够物理访问目标系统或通过网络访问共享的可移动介质即可利用，可能造成系统配置信息、密码文件或加密密钥等机密数据泄露。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0594"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.013","remediation":"通过本地安全策略设置，为\"计算机配置→Windows 设置→安全设置→本地策略→用户权利指派\"中的\"从可移动媒体访问\"项限制为仅授权管理员；同时修改注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon 中的 AllocateCDRoms 和 AllocateFloppies 值为 1，限制非管理员用户访问可移动媒体驱动器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1294","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0594","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0594.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-788r-28g9-93jm/GHSA-788r-28g9-93jm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0594.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86242/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0871.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0870","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0870.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0593","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Winlogon 关闭系统无需登录漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的 Winlogon 注册表项中 ShutdownWithoutLogon 键值默认设置为启用，允许拥有物理接触权限的未授权用户直接关闭系统而无需登录认证。该漏洞源于系统默认安全配置不当，攻击者仅需物理访问目标主机即可触发关机操作，导致系统可用性受损。影响 Windows NT 系列系统，CVSS 评分 4.9，危害等级中危。建议管理员通过注册表或组策略禁用此功能以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.9,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0593"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.887","remediation":"在注册表 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon` 中将 `ShutdownWithoutLogon` 值设为 `0`（REG_SZ），或通过组策略「计算机配置→Windows 设置→安全设置→本地策略→安全选项」启用「关闭系统：仅允许已登录的用户使用关机权限」。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/59333","http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc722469.aspx","http://www.microsoft.com/technet/archive/winntas/deploy/confeat/06wntpcc.mspx?mfr=true","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1291","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0593","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0593.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0593.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3jjv-7mh3-jr9j/GHSA-3jjv-7mh3-jr9j.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86243/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"